plot: Ben and Leslie go to Ben's hometown in Minnesota so he can get the key to the city, an honor given to all former mayors of the town except Ben, councilman Jamm sues Ron for punching him, and Chris and Ann try to test their compatibility.

Partridge - In this episode, Ben and Leslie return to Partridge so that he can receive a key to the city where he was mayor, but a kidney stone results in Leslie taking his place. Meanwhile, Jamm sues Ron for punching him at Leslie's wedding.
